metadata.name: Not as Cool Inside
metadata.description:
We are so conversant with the statement "Appearance is not reality" 
But in reality, we tend to be carried away by just what we see, hear and feel without really paying attention to the underlying state which is most times hidden by the surface appearance. 
If we could only go a bit deeper we may find out things we never thought were, and by so doing, help people when they face some challenges that they have no courage to talk about. 
Showing real concern will make this world a better place.
